Perfect, Shalini â€” given your background (10 years IT, 4 in test automation, strong in Selenium + BDD + pytest), the interviewer will expect that you understand **Playwright** not just syntactically, but conceptually â€” especially how it improves upon Selenium, how to structure robust test frameworks, and how to integrate Playwright with **pytest**, **fixtures**, and **parallel execution**.

